# Long-cache content-addressed bundles. Vite hashes every emitted
# entry, chunk, and asset under `_build/` — `assertHashedAssetNames`
# in `vite.config.ts` fails the build if a future config tweak ever
# drops `[hash]` from the output templates, so this prefix is safe
# to mark `immutable`.
#
# Everything else inherits Cloudflare's default
# `Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate`, which keeps
# HTML shells (and anything else not under `_build/`) revalidating
# every request.

/_build/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
